                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step-3:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Now select the scheme, click on the ‘Apply’ button and an application page will open."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step-4:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Click on \"Apply New\" button and submit a new application."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step-5:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Click on the \"Update Application\" button to add corrections to the application."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step-6: ",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Once the application is done, confirm it."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "Step-7:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " Take a print out of the online application and submit it to the Gram Sevak/BTM/ATM/Project Director-Aatma with the necessary documents listed in the application."
